H0.text: Net force is the term for the combined forces acting on an object.

H1.text: Total impact is the term for the combined forces acting on an object.

H2.text: Blunt force is the term for the combined forces acting on an object.

H3.text: Critical force is the term for the combined forces acting on an object.

A4.text: In mechanics, the net force is the sum of all the forces acting on an object.
